verbose_text: Our recent pilot study suggested potential benefits of Qigong exercise through changes in inflammation status, in which the results showed a significant decrease in serum level of TNF-alpha from 13.8 +/- 0.6 to 12.3 +/- 1.6 (p < 0.05) that was significantly correlated with changes in sleep quality and serum TNF-alpha level (R 2 = 0.62) [XREF_BIBR].
